version_description:
1. Special Promotion: The Monkey King - Wukong;
2. Lunar Revel Event;
3. New Heroes: Wukong, Green, Diana, Minotaur;
4. New Troops: Harbinger of Fire, Paladin, Meteor Golem, Templar Knight;
5.  Hero Chest and Troop Chests unlock time optimization.

1. Add new Player's Experience (exp) system;
2. Add save multiple formations feature;
3. Unlock new expedition chapter 5;
4. Enabling to see previous season history of clans' ranking;
5. Allowing players to see opponent's Hero with the new skin.
6. Combat balance of VooDoo Dolls' ability (can 100% kill only troops of same level and less).

In order to bring everyone a better game experience, we have made the following adjustments:
1. Added more useful details to the troop description;
2. Headhunt: players only need to battle 4 rounds instead of 8 (reduced by 50%) and can get the same amount of resources;
3. Added progress rewards to the Card Master event;
4. Added God of War points to the personal information of players with God of War badges.

1. New feature: player's avatar will have frames;
2. Troops Recruit Chests (purchasable in the shop): Improved Rewards;
3. Bugs Fixed

1.New Badges added in Profile Page
-Badge for the Arena Ranking was extend to broader rankings;
-Badge for the experience level;
-Extended badge for heroes: now include level 17 heroes
2. Some minor bug fixes, including:
-Unnecessary notification about completing quest in the Experience Quest menu.

1. Personal formation display added on profile page
2. Bug fixes
-The Orc Hunters don’t die after resurrection;
-Goblikazes don’t die;
-Part of problems concerning Daily Tasks;
-Part of problems concerning Hero Trials.

1. Optimization and improvements of the personal profile's loading speed;
2. Heroes page: improvement of the heroes animations.
3. Added a new launch screen for the game.
